Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  你把葡萄果醬全部吃光了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得千影姐做給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是愛吃也不能吃太多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直都在強調著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不是和小鈴姐一提到紅豆大福一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:32.99,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很喜歡紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也很喜歡燒魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這島上已經幾天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡一定鬧翻天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要一直在這個島上生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那邊就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  只有用最後的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回可要好好完成人工呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  幸虧醒過來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家由於擔心雪乃而聚集起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太專注摘葡萄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果腳下打滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們擔心了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不用特意摔到別人的身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家都把雪乃當作自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  要說的話  我就像大家的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會說好話  小貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我們也會有這種感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我稍微能有些察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人都聽得懂動物的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  一般來說都不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你不能和動物交談嗎）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:18.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（讀寫算是基本哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  等等…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  熊熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  剛才還一起摘葡萄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說熊熊肯定會第一個衝出來救雪乃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很貪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在附近閒逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  來幫忙尋找熊熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡分為兩隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  那樣效率會比較高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和行人找這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐和大家去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:05:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯人數很不平衡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會啦  約會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道約會的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實剛才在這附近還和熊熊在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  稍微注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淑女的臉受傷了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你自己走不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是腳印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道是熊熊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  只要跟著腳印很快就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  普通都會注意到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是熊熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為熊熊是和我差不多年齡的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這種大叔完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼看都和熊熊一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是行人一直盯著看才生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這腳印原來是那大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺食慾很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是和麻知姐一樣年齡的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊的臉更圓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起漂亮系不如說是可愛系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮系？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看上去外表很像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仔細看  就會發覺其實是女生臉的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少…年？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大家無論年齡  臉  外形都完全和熊熊不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然會有那麼多熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒有見到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部有彎月牙花紋的熊很少見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有那麼明顯的標誌的話  為什麼不早點說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己幾乎都沒走過什麼路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被捲入奇怪的事情裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這島上的女孩子們都是自我主義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正我也習慣這種狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我責駡熊熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為熊熊把做好放置在那的葡萄果醬全部吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就對她說了  「不能成為像小鈴姐那樣的貪吃鬼」這樣過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是過分的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說熊熊  去哪裡鬧彆扭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我是感覺不會因為這麼小的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你和熊熊的關係最好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在關係好的朋友裡是不分一二的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  論交往時間的話  我和熊熊是最長的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我還只會玩耍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴姐她們都已經開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是六歲的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此以前我一直以為一個人玩是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從和熊熊相遇後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像一開始去捅蜂巢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河裡抓鮭魚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了擁有好身材而舒展身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人偷偷一起化妝等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都和熊熊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此後和許多動物的關係也處的很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊轉眼就長的比我大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看她這樣  很膽小的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也許迷路了  正為難著  在哭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然裝作姐姐那樣很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實一直都在擔心著熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～熊熊去哪裡了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然  幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空哭的話  還不如抓緊去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺刺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該在這個世界上存在的邪惡的殺氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不應該在這個世界上存在的邪惡的殺氣」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是指那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡已經百年不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴  覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每天都見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  那邊的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不應該在這個世界上存在的邪惡的殺氣」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我就當作是誇獎的話心存感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音就是這樣一個傻到腦筋大條的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  都不要出手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我和鈴之間冤家路窄的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很忙  等下再陪你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這居高臨下的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這連眼睛都無法捕捉到的快速移動的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的動作太多了  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃一直都像這樣被大家保護著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排也保護著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  行人也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  小貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人他並不是在保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  行人畫的好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是發表感歎的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏  和熊熊很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請問這只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼突然…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島上是沒有男孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以第一次看到行人的話  就連熊也會吃驚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衡  這樣變裝就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  還以為動物很容易親近…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣打扮的話  不就更可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然熊熊生我的氣了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  居然這麼難找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是離家出走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找到熊熊就是絕對不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是離家出走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對不行」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上絕對沒有「絕對不行」的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…也許不能說「絕對」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這樣想的我  已經輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果自己都不相信自己的力量  怎麼能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對找出熊熊給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是畫的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們的…朋•友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥•伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這隻熊的朋•友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止都還OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難得畫的肖像畫都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問小動物的話  就不會打飛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這畫也許不是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡有像月牙一樣的標誌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個名叫熊熊的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年齡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雪乃一樣11歲左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說漂亮系  還不如是可愛系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃  這位大叔說在那邊看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個就當作回禮給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…「行行」是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊好像沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在那橋對面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是不是有點太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  行人對高處不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我一個人去好了  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雪乃  跑著是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人把我帶到這裡了  我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  橋塌了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道謝的話  還早了點吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  倒過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  讓人那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到熊熊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很擔心  一直尋找著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果是互相在找對方  而迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還一直以為熊熊離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  雪乃  如她所說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你從剛才就能聽懂熊熊的話了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說起來  我能和動物交流了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是習慣這島的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始行行也是我們的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不要啦  我才不想習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.12,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE7A573}暖和的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是最親近的炸豬排的話  還是除了「噗」以外什麼都聽不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  炸豬排的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也只能聽懂「噗」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溺水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這回一定要好好地做——人工呼吸！
